Anonymous users: allow 3 queries (tracked client-side via localStorage). After limit hit, show inline soft prompt: 'Create a free account to keep going — no credit card, ever.' Conversation context is preserved through the auth flow.

Onboarding bonus: first 7 days after signup, Casual users get 15 queries/day instead of 5. Drops to standard 5/day on day 8.

API response shape for rate limit state:
  { remaining: number, resets_at: ISO8601 string, tier: 'anon'|'casual'|'spike' }

